ackends by construction (PURE INTEGER); pure compute over Storage SSBOs + compute->compute barriers + ReadBuffer — NO convex-poly MERGING beyond triangles / detail mesh (deferred), NO A* (NAV5), NO new RHI; NAV1''s nav_raster + nav_spans golden + NAV2''s nav_filter/nav_distance + nav_distfield golden + NAV3''s nav_region + nav_regions golden + the FLOAT engine/physics/ + engine/sim/fpx.h UNTOUCHED (nav is additive + parallel; navmesh.h #includes fpx.h read-only for FloorDiv))
